title: Bruising noted in actress Natalie Wood's autopsy report: Does the pattern prove domestic abuse?
itunes:title: Bruising noted in actress Natalie Wood's autopsy report: Does the pattern prove domestic abuse?
description:
Beautiful actress Natalie Wood drowns during a weekend boat trip to Catalina Island. Although no one has ever been charged in her death, sister Lana Wood says something sinister was going on behind the scenes. Her autopsy report shows bruising that some experts say is not consistent with falling off a boat. Was Natalie Wood a victim of domestic abuse?

An all-star panel joins Nancy Grace to discuss the case today:

Lana Wood: Natalie's Sister, Actress 

Marti Rulli: Author of "Goodbye Natalie, Goodbye Splendour" 

Sheryl McCollum: Forensics Expert & Cold Case Investigative Research Institute Founder
